openstack

This is the openstack module.

Global Variables 

* api_bind_ip : facter vairables , default is $::ipaddress .
   if eth0 if binded , use $::ipaddress_eth0 instead .

* mysql_bind_ip : mysql bind-address in my.cnf 
    if not specified , api_bind_ip will be used . 
    if api_bind_ip not specified , $::ipaddress will be the default.

* rabbitmq_bind_ip : rabbitmq bind ipaddress 
    if not specified , api_bind_ip will be used.
    if api_bind_ip not specified , $::ipaddress will be the default.

* novncproxy_base_ip : nova.conf 
     novcproxy_base_ip, nova get-vnc-console will use this ip to connectio to vnc






